trans-unit.source: The <embeddedLabel>Structure</embeddedLabel> section in a JSON file that defines an Azure Data Factory table contains a collection of columns for the table.
trans-unit.target: The <embeddedLabel>Structure</embeddedLabel> section in a JSON file that defines an Azure Data Factory table contains a collection of columns for the table.

trans-unit.source: Each column contains the following properties:
trans-unit.target: Each column contains the following properties:

trans-unit.source: <embeddedLabel>Supported data types:</embeddedLabel> String, Int, Decimal, Guid, Boolean and Date.
trans-unit.target: <embeddedLabel>Supported data types:</embeddedLabel> String, Int, Decimal, Guid, Boolean and Date.
